<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=1080, height=1350" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#0b1220;
      --ink:#f8fafc;
      --muted: rgba(248,250,252,0.82);
      --stroke: rgba(248,250,252,0.14);
      --accent:#f97316;
      --accent2:#a78bfa;
      --pad:86px;
      --r:30px;
    }
    *{ box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0; }
    body{
      background: var(--bg);
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      color: var(--ink);
    }
    .slide{
      width:1080px; height:1350px; overflow:hidden; position:relative;
      padding: var(--pad);
      background:
        radial-gradient(820px 720px at 16% 18%, rgba(167,139,250,0.22) 0%, rgba(167,139,250,0.04) 55%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 70%),
        radial-gradient(760px 760px at 86% 82%, rgba(249,115,22,0.18) 0%, rgba(249,115,22,0.04) 52%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 70%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #0b1220 0%, #070b14 100%);
    }
    .banner{
      border-radius: var(--r);
      border: 1px solid var(--stroke);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      padding: 22px 24px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }
    .tag{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 0.10em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(248,250,252,0.86);
    }
    .chip{
      width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(249,115,22,0.12);
    }
    .idx{
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: rgba(248,250,252,0.78);
    }
    .page{
      height: calc(1350px - var(--pad)*2);
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
    }
    .headline{
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 92px;
      line-height: 1.03;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      overflow-wrap:anywhere;
      word-break:break-word;
      max-width: 920px;
    }
    .copy{
      margin-top: 22px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 38px;
      line-height: 1.46;
      color: var(--muted);
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      overflow-wrap:anywhere;
      word-break:break-word;
      max-width: 940px;
    }
    .callout{
      margin-top:auto;
      border-radius: var(--r);
      border: 1px solid rgba(248,250,252,0.16);
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249,115,22,0.16), rgba(167,139,250,0.14));
      padding: 26px 26px 24px;
    }
    .callout h3{
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: rgba(248,250,252,0.92);
    }
    .callout p{
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.42;
      color: rgba(248,250,252,0.92);
      white-space: pre-wrap;
    }
    .cta .headline{ font-size: 104px; }
    .cta .copy{ font-size: 40px; }
    .handle{
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 38px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: rgba(248,250,252,0.96);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="slide cover">
    <div class="page">
      <div class="banner">
        <div class="tag"><span class="chip"></span> Cover</div>
        <div class="idx">{{slide_index}} / {{slide_total}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="headline">{{joinEmojiOrphans cover_slide.headline}}</div>
      {{#if cover_slide.body}}<div class="copy">{{joinEmojiOrphans cover_slide.body}}</div>{{/if}}
      <div class="callout">
        <h3>Why this matters</h3>
        <p>It’s not “deep”. It’s actionable. Save it so you can use it mid-conversation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {{#each body_slides}}
  <div class="slide body-slide">
    <div class="page">
      <div class="banner">
        <div class="tag"><span class="chip"></span> Body</div>
        <div class="idx">{{../slide_index}} / {{../slide_total}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="headline" style="font-size:78px">{{joinEmojiOrphans headline}}</div>
      <div class="copy">{{joinEmojiOrphans body}}</div>
      <div class="callout">
        <h3>Try saying</h3>
        <p>“I’m noticing a pattern. Can we slow down and name what we both need?”</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{/each}}

  <div class="slide cta">
    <div class="page">
      <div class="banner">
        <div class="tag"><span class="chip"></span> CTA</div>
        <div class="idx">{{slide_index}} / {{slide_total}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="headline">{{#if cta_text}}{{joinEmojiOrphans cta_text}}{{else}}{{joinEmojiOrphans cta_slide.body}}{{/if}}</div>
      {{#if cta_slide.sub}}<div class="copy">{{joinEmojiOrphans cta_slide.sub}}</div>{{/if}}
      {{#if cta_handle}}<div class="handle">{{cta_handle}}</div>{{else}}{{#if cta_slide.handle}}<div class="handle">{{cta_slide.handle}}</div>{{/if}}{{/if}}
      <div class="callout">
        <h3>Engage</h3>
        <p>Comment your sign and what you want more of in love: clarity, consistency, or depth.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

